Initial setup

- Install Node.js
	- In your terminal
			git clone git://github.com/ry/node.git
			cd node
			./configure
			make
			sudo make install

- Install Redis
	- In your terminal
			wget http://redis.googlecode.com/files/redis-1.2.5.tar.gz
			tar xzvf redis-1.2.5.tar.gz
			cd redis-1.2.5
			make
			sudo mv redis-server /usr/bin/
			sudo mv redis-cli /usr/bin/

- Install Chalk Graffiti
	- In your terminal
			git clone git://github.com/maryrosecook/chalkgraffiti
			cd chalkgraffiti
			node server.js
	- In your web browser
			- Visit http://localhost:3000